data.description: Picture yourself in this charming home. Overlooking a large yard in fabulous West Palm Beach. Close to shopping, minutes from the highway and a short drive to the lively downtown area and pristine beach! Tastefully updated 3 bedroom/ 2 bath with a Large Den. Newly renovated kitchen, with shaker cabinets, with lots of storage and a spice rack drawer. Farm sink and new appliances. New laminate floors throughout the home. Lots of closets and storage. 2 Sheds in the back. Front room can be converted to a rental for extra income. Fenced yard with a gate to accommodate a boat Great parking for the boat. NEW Roof 2023 with transferable Warranty from roofer. Make your appointment today to see it.
